"use strict";(self.webpackChunksuprema_docs=self.webpackChunksuprema_docs||[]).push([["46003"],{20907(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"2026-06-changelog","metadata":{"permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-06-changelog","source":"@site/i18n/ja/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-06-changelog.md","title":"June 2026","description":"Provides the major update history for Suprema Docs in June 2026.","date":"2026-07-01T12:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"title":"June 2026","description":"Provides the major update history for Suprema Docs in June 2026.","slug":"2026-06-changelog","date":"2026-07-01T12:00","isTranslationMissing":false},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"May 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-05-changelog"}},"content":"This June, **Suprema Docs** is packed with major news. Suprema\'s new video security product, **AI Camera ViOnyx**, has been launched with its installation manual and web server manual now available. In addition, the **BioStar X Mobile** manual for managing access control systems from your smartphone, and the **BioStar X Security Hardening Guide** for enhancing system security, have also been newly published. Check them out now.\\n\\n![Suprema Docs 26.06 Changelogs](/img/changelogs/changelogs-202606.png)\\n\\n{/* truncate */}\\n\\n## Document Hub Launch\\n\\n![](/img/changelogs/document_hub_banner_en.png)\\n\\n[**Document Hub**](../dochub) is now open \u2014 your one-stop destination to download manuals, release notes, drilling templates, and A&E specifications for all Suprema products.\\n\\n## AI Camera\\n\\nAdded manuals for ViOnyx, Suprema\'s new video security product.\\n\\n* [ViOnyx Installation Manual](../device/vionyx/)\\n\\n* [ViOnyx Web Server Manual](../device/vionyx_webserver/)\\n\\n## Platform\\n\\n### BioStar X\\n\\n* See the [1.0.2 Hotfix Release Notes](../platform/biostar_x/release-notes/102)\\n\\n* [Upgrading BioStar X](../platform/biostar_x/migration-x): Added minimum system requirements information for upgrades\\n\\n* [BioStar X API](../developer/bsxapi) documentation revamped\\n\\n### BioStar X Mobile\\n\\nThe [BioStar X Mobile](../platform/biostar_x_mobile) app user manual has been newly added. It covers features including user registration, remote door control, real-time event monitoring, and alert handling on mobile devices.\\n\\n### BioStar Air\\n\\nAdded guidance on credential reissuance\\n\\n* [Manage Users](../platform/biostar_air/user-management-user-list#manageUserStatus)\\n\\n* [Troubleshooting Mobile Cards](../platform/biostar_air/troubleshooting-suprema-pass-app#mobileCardDeleted)\\n\\n## Devices\\n\\n### Device Updates\\n\\n* [BioStation 3 Max](../device/biostation_3_max/)\\n  \\n  * Updated [Master Admin](../device/biostation_3_max/getting-started) content\\n  \\n  * Updated [Product Specifications](../device/biostation_3_max/product-specifications)\\n  \\n* [BioStation 3](../device/biostation_3/)\\n  \\n  * Updated [wall mount bracket image](../device/biostation_3/getting-started)\\n\\n  * Updated [Master Admin](../device/biostation_3/getting-started) content\\n  \\n  * Added [tilting bracket installation](../device/biostation_3/installation) instructions\\n  \\n  * Updated [Product Specifications](../device/biostation_3/product-specifications)\\n\\n* [X-Station 2](../device/xstation_2/)\\n\\n  * Updated [Master Admin](../device/xstation_2/getting-started) content\\n  \\n  * Updated [Camera QR support](../device/xstation_2/authentication) content\\n  \\n  * Updated [Product Specifications](../device/xstation_2/product-specifications)\\n  \\n* [BioStation 2a](../device/biostation_2a/)\\n  \\n  * Updated [Master Admin](../device/biostation_2a/getting-started) content\\n  \\n  * Updated [Product Specifications](../device/biostation_2a/product-specifications)\\n\\n* [BioLite N2](../device/biolite_n2/)\\n\\n  * Updated [Master Admin](../device/biolite_n2/getting-started) content\\n  \\n  * Updated [Product Specifications](../device/biolite_n2/product-specifications)\\n\\n* Product Specifications updated\\n\\n  * [XPass 2](../device/xpass_2/product-specifications)\\n\\n  * [XPass D2](../device/xpass_d2/product-specifications)\\n\\n  * [BioEntry W3](../device/bioentry_w3/product-specifications)\\n\\n### Release Notes\\n\\n* [Door Interface](../device/doorinterface/release-notes/103): Added release notes for version 1.0.3\\n\\n* [ViOnyx](../device/vionyx/release-notes/101): Added release notes for version 1.0.1\\n\\n* [BioEntry W3](../device/bioentry_w3/release-notes/103): Added release notes for version 1.0.3\\n\\n## How-To Guides\\n\\n### Master Admin\\n\\n[Master Admin Setup Guide](../how-to/master-admin): Revised overall master administrator content and added device placement information for CE-compliant products\\n\\n### BioStar X Security Hardening\\n\\nThe [BioStar X Hardening Guide](../how-to/bsx_hardening/) is now available. It provides step-by-step practical recommendations for enhancing access control system security, including server hardening, network firewall configuration, and patch management.\\n\\n## Integrations\\n\\n[Genetec](../integration/genetec/): Updated system management content"},{"id":"2026-05-changelog","metadata":{"permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-05-changelog","source":"@site/i18n/ja/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-05-changelog.md","title":"May 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs in May 2026.","date":"2026-05-28T12:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"title":"May 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs in May 2026.","slug":"2026-05-changelog","date":"2026-05-28T12:00","isTranslationMissing":false},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"June 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-06-changelog"},"nextItem":{"title":"April 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-04-changelog"}},"content":"This May, **Suprema Docs** expanded in both scope and scale. The new device **BioStation 3 Max** has joined the lineup, and BioStar X and BioStar Air have received significant feature enhancements. Don\'t miss the highlight of this month\u2014a brand-new **Integration** category covering third-party product connectivity.\\n\\n![Suprema Docs 26.05 Changelogs](/img/changelogs/changelogs-202605.png)\\n\\n{/* truncate */}\\n\\n## Platform\\n\\n### BioStar X\\n\\n* Read the [v1.0.2 Release Notes](../platform/biostar_x/release-notes/102)\\n\\n* [Change the Main Server IP Address](../platform/biostar_x/change-ip): Added instructions for changing the BioStar X main server IP address\\n\\n* [Directory Integration Settings](../platform/biostar_x/settings-diretory-integration): Added **Add/Update/Delete** modes to directory service integration settings\\n\\n* [System Restore](../platform/biostar_x/settings-system-system-restore): Updated detailed procedures for using the restore tool\\n\\n* [Delete Event Logs from Device](../platform/biostar_x/settings-device-using-functions#deleteLogsFromDevice): Added the feature to delete event logs stored on the device\\n\\n* [Integrate VMS](../platform/biostar_x/settings-video-integration): Added support for **Nx Witness v6.x.x**\\n\\n* [Set Up the Camera](../platform/biostar_x/settings-videos-camera#addCameraPermission): Added instructions for configuring camera group permission settings\\n\\n* Added support specifications for BioStation 3 Max and XPass Q2 devices\\n\\n### BioStar Air\\n\\n* Read the [SW v2.12 Release Notes](../platform/biostar_air/release-notes/bsair-release-notes#2120)\\n\\n* [Install Airfob Patch](../platform/biostar_air/install-airfob-patch): Added instructions for installing the Airfob patch\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Devices\\n\\n### New Devices\\n\\nThe manual for BioStation 3 Max, Suprema\'s flagship AI-based biometric device, is now available.\\n\\n* [BioStation 3 Max](../device/biostation_3_max)\\n\\n### Device Updates\\n\\n* Applied v1.0.2 update for [BioEntry W3](../device/bioentry_w3/)\\n\\n  * Updated wall mount bracket images\\n\\n  * Added [RS-485 usage precautions](../device/bioentry_w3/getting-started#cable)\\n\\n* Applied v1.2.3 update for [Device Manager](../device/device_manager/)\\n\\n  * [Set Up XPass D2](../device/device_manager/xpd2-settings): Added **Enforce EV2/EV3 Secure Messaging** feature\\n\\n### Device Release Notes\\n\\n* [BioEntry R2](../device/bioentry_r2/release-notes/142): Added v1.4.2 Release Notes\\n\\n* [CoreStation](../device/corestation_40/release-notes/172): Added v1.7.2 Release Notes\\n\\n* [CoreStation 20](../device/corestation_20/release-notes/104): Added v1.0.4 Release Notes\\n\\n* [BioEntry W3](../device/bioentry_w3/release-notes/102): Added v1.0.2 Release Notes\\n\\n* [Device Manager](../device/device_manager/release-notes/123): Added v1.2.3 Release Notes\\n\\n* [FaceStation F2](../device/facestation_f2/release-notes/222): Added v2.2.2 Release Notes\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Integration\\n\\nWe\'ve added a new **Integration** category. Check out how to integrate third-party products with Suprema devices.\\n\\n* [Genetec](../integration/genetec/)\\n\\n* [Gallagher](../integration/gallagher/)\\n\\n* [Software House](../integration/ccure/)"},{"id":"2026-04-changelog","metadata":{"permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-04-changelog","source":"@site/i18n/ja/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-changelog.md","title":"April 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs in April 2026.","date":"2026-05-01T12:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"title":"April 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs in April 2026.","slug":"2026-04-changelog","date":"2026-05-01T12:00","isTranslationMissing":false},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"May 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-05-changelog"},"nextItem":{"title":"March 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-03-changelog"}},"content":"April was a busy month for **Suprema Docs** with new updates across platforms, devices, and developer APIs. Explore the changes we\'ve made this month.\\n\\n![Suprema Docs 26.04 Changelogs](/img/changelogs-202604.png)\\n\\n{/* truncate */}\\n\\n## Platform\\n\\n### BioStar X\\n\\n* [Integrate VMS](../platform/biostar_x/settings-video-integration#install-vms-certification): Added example paths for certificate installation\\n\\n* [Server Detailed Settings](../platform/biostar_x/settings-server-server#custom-field): Added clarification that no file format restrictions are applied when custom user fields are set as file upload options\\n\\n* [Video License](../platform/biostar_x/licensing#features-add-ons): Updated documentation\\n\\n### BioStar Air\\n\\n* Updated BioStar Air [v2.12 firmware release notes](../platform/biostar_air/release-notes/firmware)\\n\\n* Restructured BioStar Air release notes documentation\\n\\n  * [Software Release Notes](../platform/biostar_air/release-notes/software)\\n\\n  * [Firmware Release Notes](../platform/biostar_air/release-notes/firmware)\\n\\n## Devices\\n\\nAdded new release notes and updated device documentation.\\n\\n* [XPass Q2 Installation Guide](../device/xpass_q2): Newly created\\n\\n* [XPass D2](../device/xpass_d2/release-notes/183): Added v1.8.3 release notes\\n\\n* [BioStation 2a](../device/biostation_2a/release-notes/121): Added v1.2.1 release notes\\n\\n* [X-Station 2](../device/xstation_2/release-notes/141): Added v1.4.1 release notes\\n\\n* [BioLite N2](../device/biolite_n2/release-notes/171): Added v1.7.1 release notes\\n\\n* [BioStation 3](../device/biostation_3/release-notes/143): Added v1.4.3 release notes\\n\\n* [XPass 2](../device/xpass_2/release-notes/152): Added v1.5.2 release notes\\n\\n## Developer\\n\\n* Updated API documentation: [Export as CSV API](../developer/bsxapi?api=export-as-csv)"},{"id":"2026-03-changelog","metadata":{"permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-03-changelog","source":"@site/i18n/ja/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-03-changelog.md","title":"March 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs from February through March.","date":"2026-04-08T12:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"title":"March 2026","description":"Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs from February through March.","slug":"2026-03-changelog","date":"2026-04-08T12:00","isTranslationMissing":false},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"April 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-04-changelog"},"nextItem":{"title":"January 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog"}},"content":"This March update improves your **Suprema Docs** experience with a more intuitive interface and enhanced search functionality. Meanwhile, the BioStar Air Administrator Guide has been completely restructured to help you understand all features\u2014from user management to access control and video surveillance\u2014at a glance.\\n\\n![Suprema Docs 26.03 Changelogs](/img/changelogs-202603.png)\\n\\n{/* truncate */}\\n\\n## Docs\\n\\n* Redesigned home page\\n\\n  ![Suprema Docs home](/img/changelogs/changelog-03-home.png)\\n\\n* Enhanced search functionality\\n\\n  Added product-specific search and keyboard shortcut (Ctrl + K) to open the search bar\\n\\n  ![Suprema Docs home](/img/changelogs/changelog-03-search.png)\\n\\n## Platform\\n\\n### BioStar X\\n\\n* Updated documentation for [VMS Server Integration and Certificate Installation](../platform/biostar_x/settings-video-integration)\\n\\n### BioStar Air\\n\\n* Completed comprehensive restructuring and optimization of the [BioStar Air Administrator Guide](../platform/biostar_air/)\\n\\n* Expanded multilingual support for BioStar Air: English, Japanese, and Spanish translations added\\n\\n  * Added documentation for key features including user management, access rights management, and video management\\n\\n  * Added English interface images and user interface screenshots\\n\\n* Improved BioStar Air table of contents structure and reorganized sections\\n\\n## Devices\\n\\nAdded new release notes and updated existing device documentation.\\n\\n### Device Documentation Updates\\n\\n* [XPass 2](../device/xpass_2/release-notes/151): Added v1.5.1 release notes\\n\\n\x3c!-- * [BioEntry W3](../device/biostation_3_max/): Added v1.0.2 release notes --\x3e\\n\\n* [Device Manager](../device/device_manager/release-notes/122): Established new app release notes category and added v1.2.2 release notes\\n\\n* [BioEntry P2](../device/bioentry_p2/release-notes/160): Added v1.6.0 release notes\\n\\n* Added instructional images for device factory reset button location\\n\\n## Developer\\n\\n* API documentation updated: [Create BioStar X QR](../developer/bsxapi?api=create-biostar-x-qr)\\n\\n* Device SDK: Added v2.9.12 release notes\\n\\n## Multilingual Support\\n\\n* Improved documentation quality for Japanese and Spanish versions\\n\\n  * Enhanced consistency of document titles and content\\n\\n  * Corrected mistranslations and standardized terminology\\n\\n  * Fixed spacing and grammar issues\\n\\n* Significantly updated English translation\\n\\n  * Standardized technical terminology\\n\\n  * Improved sentence structure and phrasing\\n\\n## Open Source Software Licenses\\n\\n* Added license attributions: [BSD-2-Clause](../legal/open-source-licenses#the-2-clause-bsd-license), [BSD-3-Clause](../legal/open-source-licenses#the-3-clause-bsd-license), [EPL](../legal/open-source-licenses#eclipse-public-license), [EDL](../legal/open-source-licenses#eclipse-distribution-license), [LGPLv2.1](../legal/open-source-licenses#gnu-lesser-general-public-v21-license)\u200B, [GPLv2](../legal/open-source-licenses#gnu-general-public-v2-license)\u200B, [ISC](../legal/open-source-licenses#isc-license), [zlib](../legal/open-source-licenses#zlib-license)"},{"id":"2026-01-02-changelog","metadata":{"permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog","source":"@site/i18n/ja/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-02-changelog.md","title":"January 2026","description":"Provides an overview of updates since the initial launch of Suprema Docs through December.","date":"2026-01-02T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"title":"January 2026","description":"Provides an overview of updates since the initial launch of Suprema Docs through December.","slug":"2026-01-02-changelog","isTranslationMissing":false},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"March 2026","permalink":"/docs/ja/changelog/2026-03-changelog"}},"content":"**Suprema Docs** is a knowledge hub that brings together all product manuals and technical documentation in one place. It includes the following key documentation:\\n\\n* **Product manuals**: Installation and user manuals for Suprema products\\n\\n* **Solution manuals**\\n\\n  * User manual for BioStar X\\n\\n  * User manual for BioStar Air (coming soon)\\n\\n* **Technical documents**: APIs and other technical resources\\n\\n* **Release Notes**\\n\\nBelow is a summary of the key updates for January 2026.\\n\\n![Suprema Docs](/img/changelogs-202501.png)\\n\\n{/* truncate */}\\n\\n## BioStar X\\n\\n* Added [BioStar X v1.0.1 Release Notes](../platform/biostar_x/release-notes/101)\\n\\n* Added guide for [IR Face](../platform/biostar_x/enroll-credential-ir-face) credentials\\n\\n* Added guide for [Remote Access](../platform/biostar_x/settings-remote-access) configuration and usage\\n\\n* Added guide for integrating event logs using the [Virtual Device](../platform/biostar_x/settings-virtual-device-event-log) feature\\n\\n* Updated guides for the ability to enter a reason when exporting or printing user, data, and audit trail menus\\n\\n  * [Export/Import User Information](../platform/biostar_x/export-import-user-info)\\n\\n  * [Generate Report](../platform/biostar_x/data-generate-reports)\\n\\n  * [Manage Audit Trail](../platform/biostar_x/settings-system-audit-trail)\\n\\n* Updated [License Policy](../platform/biostar_x/licensing) details\\n\\n  * Added description that devices cannot be added without a Base License\\n\\n  * Added description of limit on the number of Ethernet-connected devices\\n\\n  * Added description of maximum administrator count\\n\\n* Added [BioStar X API](../developer/bsxapi) documentation\\n\\n* Added [BioStar X License Calculator](../bsx-license-calculator) page to help with complex licensing requirements\\n\\n## Devices\\n\\nUpdated all the latest device manuals. The device manuals available in **Suprema Docs** are as follows:\\n\\n### Biometric Devices\\n\\n* [BioEntry W3](../device/bioentry_w3/)\\n* [BioStation 2a](../device/biostation_2a)\\n* [BioStation 3](../device/biostation_3)\\n* [FaceStation F2](../device/facestation_f2)\\n* [FaceStation 2](../device/facestation_2)\\n* [BioLite N2](../device/biolite_n2)\\n* [BioEntry W2](../device/bioentry_w2)\\n* [BioEntry P2](../device/bioentry_p2)\\n* [BioEntry R2](../device/bioentry_r2)\\n\\n### RF/Mobile Devices\\n\\n* [X-Station 2](../device/xstation_2)\\n* [XPass 2](../device/xpass_2)\\n* [XPass D2](../device/xpass_d2)\\n* [XPass S2](../device/xpass_s2)\\n\\n### Intelligent Controller\\n\\n* [CoreStation 20](../device/corestation_20)\\n* [CoreStation](../device/corestation_40)\\n* [Enclosure](../device/enclosure)\\n\\n### Peripherals\\n\\n* [Door Interface](../device/doorinterface)\\n* [Input Module](../device/inputmodule)\\n* [Output Module](../device/outputmodule)\\n* [Door Module](../device/doormodule)\\n* [Secure Module](../device/securemodule)\\n* [Extended Module](../device/extendedmodule)\\n* [Extended Module-SC](../device/extendedmodule_sc)\\n\\n### APPS\\n\\n* [Device Manager](../device/device_manager)\\n* [CoreStation Setup Manager](../device/corestation_setup_manager)\\n\\n## What\u2019s next and expected benefits\\n\\n**Suprema Docs** will continue to evolve. We will keep updating the content to improve completeness and quality, so it better meets the needs of our customers and partners. Internally, it will also help you quickly share accurate information needed for product development, technical support, and sales activities. We also plan to expand multilingual support in the near future. Documentation in Japanese and Spanish will be released soon."}]}}')}}]);